title: Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate 3/18/09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




March 18, 2009

 



Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate 3/18/09




THE WHITE HOUSE   Office of the Press Secretary  __________________________________________________________  FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE                             March 18, 2009   NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:   Ronald H. Weich, of the District of Columbia, to be an Assistant Attorney General, vice William Emil Moschella.
